snippet.title: Puyo Puyo~n - Longplay (English Patch)
snippet.description:
English patch: https://www.precisemuseum.com/post/697840867760832512/puyo-puyo-n-is-now-fully-playable-in-english-with

The last time I played this game (which was the last longplay for it I uploaded) was only less than 2 weeks ago, and I didn't exactly like it, it's still a 4/10

Either way, a big thank you to everyone who worked on the translation patch, it's a great patch
